# Synthetic Data License

SPDX-License-Identifier: CC0-1.0

Synthetic datasets and generated synthetic fixtures in this directory are
released under CC0 1.0 Universal unless a file says otherwise.

The data here is fictional and must not be treated as clinical, epidemiological,
or participant-level evidence. It exists so contributors can build, test,
validate, localize, and prototype open infrastructure without using real
participant data.

